<P><B>Reviews of movies major and minor by Harvey O'Brien, who teaches Film
Studies at University College Dublin and is the author of <I>The Real Ireland:
The Evolution of Ireland in Documentary Film</I> (Manchester University
Press, 2004) and co-editor of <I>Keeping it Real: Issues and Directions
in Irish Film and Television</I> (Wallflower Press, 2004). </B></P>

